Name:                haxy
Version:             1.0
x-revision: 2
Synopsis:            A simple HTTP proxy server library
Description:         A library for writing HTTP proxy servers with the focus on simplicity, flexibility and modularity. Allows arbitrary transformations on requests and responses and custom caching methods. It's up to the user to make sure that the message transformations are consistent with the HTTP specification. The package versions follow Semantic Versioning model (semver.org).
